Install VS Code Extensions: Install the recommended VS Code extensions.

(Extensions: ESLint, Prettier, Firebase Explorer, Jest Runner, GitLens, Tailwind CSS IntelliSense)

Start Development Server with Emulators: Run the combined development and emulator start script.

(Command: npm run dev:emulator)

Verify Development Environment Access: Access the development environment in your browser to ensure Next.js is running.

(URL: http://localhost:3000)

(Check for any initial errors in the browser console or terminal)